Tkinter notes

Super
--------
tk.Tk.__init__(self, *args, **kwargs)
It's the same as:
super().__init__(self, *args, **kwargs)

Fonts
--------
from tkinter import font as tkfont
widget = tkfont.Font(family="Helvetica", size=18,weight="bold",
slant="italic")
or:
widget(font("Helvetica 18 bold")

Grid
------
Grid doesn't allow to to expand the whole frame.
container = tk.Frame(self)
container.pack(side="top", fill="both",expand=True)